Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.44,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.44,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\c&H6E3C42&}Re:{\c&H060200&}从零开始的休息时间~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.77,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我真读不懂这些文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.14,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,昴你真心有些不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.30,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,明明既没有钱又看不懂文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么来到卢克尼卡的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.13,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,那是因为...该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:23.62,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,就是那个啦 就像SF轻小说一样穿越到这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:29.10,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,嘛 这种情况也是存在的 这世上充满了戏剧性...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.13,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,是吧 帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.61,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,你要是这么突然问的话 我也只能不同意你说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:36.39,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.85,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不知为何这些东西的名称跟我老家的比较像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.90,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,没准习惯了就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.15,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,是这样的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.32,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,嗯 真的是非常像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.08,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,比如说这苹果 RINGA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.96,SignA,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(350,70)}看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.94,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,在我老家称为 RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:51.09,SignA,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(350,70)}苹  果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.27,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,RIN...GO？好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.40,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说RINGA的发音才是怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:58.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,发音总有一些违和感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:01.98,SignB,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs50os(350,70)}苹  果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:02.03,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,想发出RIN!ga的声音 就是这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:01.98,SignC,Text,0,0,0,,口音!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.08,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,RINGA~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.68,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,有种要高潮了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:12.88,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,总之这里就有一种很像但又不是的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:16.78,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,呜哇...这里明明是水果店为嘛会卖青椒（pi-man）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.79,SignA,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord1\pos(293,80)\1c&H5A12CA&\3c&H5800B0&\b0}青 椒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,哦 这里叫pi-maru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,果然发音很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:25.43,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.29,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:31.75,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,莫非你很讨厌pi-man...啊不 讨厌pi-maru吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.15,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,o(*////▽////*)q
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:34.68,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,诶︿(￣︶￣)︿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:36.65,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,因为那可是pimaru啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是绿色的恶魔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.10,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,绿色的恶魔...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:43.89,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,绝大多数我是能吃的 真的 真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:46.18,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,但是只吃青椒不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.50,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,那样就只能抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.76,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,挑吃可是不好的哦 莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.47,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,帕克 我也有努力过的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.60,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,这种孩子气...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.36,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,{\an8}第一次遇到青椒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.16,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,再加上这种全力狡辩的性格...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}青椒对我抱有极大的敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.65,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,真是可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.79,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,怎么了 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不爱吃青椒这种事有那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:11.16,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,没 我觉得人讨厌一两种东西是没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.63,Default - italics,SUbaru,0,0,0,,嘛 我也不爱吃青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:17.80,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,还有番茄啊茄子啊蔓菁之类很多都不想吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.01,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,一脸囧样...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,果然对我失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.21,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不不不 才不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.18,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,喏 那副囧脸不就是很失望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.68,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,帕克 不要说些奇怪的话啊！
